channel.title: Requesting/Hiring 317 RSPS Staff
channel.description:
I am looking for some people to help me develop a RSPS. I am looking to make a 317, loading +600 items and bosses. and loading a 525 Gameframe. Please if you are interested, please add Like.A.Baus on Skype. and we can talk about it more there.
Tell me what you are good at and what you specialize in. Thanks!
